context.arch.intelligibility.weka.j48
Class J48Parser

java.lang.Object
  context.arch.intelligibility.weka.j48.J48Parser

public class J48Parser
extends java.lang.Object

Utility class to parse the decision tree model from WEKA's J48 class, and build a Disjunctions of traces (Conjunctions) from each class value. Converts proprietary TreeDOT format used by J48 to format used in Intelligibility Toolkit. In the former, nodes represent attribute names (e.g. "brightness") and edges represent conditions (e.g. "<= 5"). In the latter, nodes represent full conditions (e.g. "brightness <= 5")
